             <tr> 
              <td align="left" style="padding-top: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 40px; padding-bottom: 0px; line-height: 0px; text-align: left;" valign="top" width="418"> 
               <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 24px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size:24px"> 
                <br> Partner with the&nbsp;IRIS Internship Program
               </div> 
               <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 16px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px">
                 Consider including&nbsp;it in your next proposal
               </div> 
               <div> 
                <img align="none" alt="Interns_2013 2" border="0" height="198" hspace="0" src="https://cc286088d6-custmedia.vresp.com/53e043faff/Interns_2013%202.jpg" style="display: block; width: 371px; height: 198px;" title="Interns_2013 2" vspace="10" width="371">
               </div> 
               <div style="color: #474747; line-height: 15px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 11px"> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0"> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif;">Help inspire careers in the Earth sciences by participating in the&nbsp;IRIS Internship Program.&nbsp;This successful program, now in its sixteenth year, is primarily supported&nbsp;by a grant from the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.nsf.gov">National Science Foundation</a>. This grant provides funding for 11 interns each summer, but a total&nbsp;of 15 to 20 interns can be accommodated.&nbsp;IRIS community members are encouraged&nbsp;to include&nbsp;the Internship Program in the broader impacts section of their research proposals. Several test cases indicate&nbsp;that this arrangement&nbsp;has been effective for the&nbsp;PIs. For more information please contact <a href="mailto:hubenth@iris.edu?subject=Interest%20in%20the%20IRIS%20Internship%20Program">Michael Hubenthal</a><a href="mailto:Michael.Hubenthal@iris.edu?subject=IRIS%20Internship%20Program"> </a></span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif;">or visit&nbsp;</span><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif;">our <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/internship/hosts">website</a></span><span style="color: rgb(5, 45, 77); font-family: arial, sans-serif;">.</span></span>
                </div> 
               </div> <br> <br> 
               <div style="margin: 0 20px 10px 0; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 24px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 24px"> 
                <br> Nearly 50 People&nbsp;Visit TA Site
               </div> 
               <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 16px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px">
                 Outside of&nbsp;Washington, DC
               </div> 
               <div> 
                <img align="none" alt="TA_MD_newsletter" border="0" height="198" hspace="0" src="https://cc286088d6-custmedia.vresp.com/53e043faff/TA_MD_newsletter.jpg" style="display: block; width: 371px; height: 198px;" title="TA_MD_newsletter" vspace="10" width="371">
               </div> 
               <div style="color: #474747; line-height: 15px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0"> 
                 <span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; line-height: 15px;">With&nbsp;<a href="http://www.usarray.org/researchers/obs/transportable">EarthScope's&nbsp;Transportable Array&nbsp;</a>blanketing the Mid-Atlantic states, IRIS invited federal and state&nbsp;agency representatives,&nbsp;Capitol Hill&nbsp;staffers, and others to visit a nearby station. IRIS staff and several seismologists delivered short presentations on USArray science and program history. The day was capped by a group "jump." The recorded&nbsp;signal was shown to the visitors a few seconds later.&nbsp;To check the status of the full&nbsp;USArray, click&nbsp;<a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/static/us_array_status.php">here</a>.</span>
                </div> 
               </div> </td> 
              <td align="left" bgcolor="#cdde9f" style="padding-left: 10px; padding-right: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-top: 15px; line-height: 18px; text-align: left;" valign="top" width="200"> 
               <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/news/story/mark_your_calendars_for_the_2014_iris_workshop"><span style="color:#4b0082;"><strong>Date and Venue Set </strong> <strong><span style="font-size:8pt;">for 2014 IRIS Worskshop</span></strong></span></a>
                <br> 
                <div style="margin: 0px 0px 10px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 12px; font-size: 10px;"> 
                 <br> 
                 <span style="font-size: 8pt;">June 8–11<br> Sunriver, OR</span>
                </div> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                 <br> 
                 <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/news/story/national_science_board_unanimously_approves_development_of_a_five_year_coop"><strong><span style="color:#4b0082;">SAGE Proposal Approved</span></strong></a>
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;">The National Science Board&nbsp;unanimously approved the development of a five-year Cooperative Agreement.</span>
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                  <br> 
                  <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/news/story/iris_board_of_directors_appoints_a_nominations_committee_for_2013_elections"><strong><span style="color:#4b0082;">Nominations Committee Formed</span>&nbsp;</strong></a>
                 </div> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;">Elections for important positions on the IRIS Board of Directors will be held December 9, 2013, in San Francisco.</span>
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <span style="display: none;">&nbsp;</span>
                </div> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                 <br> 
                 <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/news/story/iris_to_begin_search_for_a_new_president"><strong><span style="color:#4b0082;">Transition Team Formed&nbsp;</span></strong></a>
                </div> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 11px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10px"> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;">After 22 years as IRIS President, David Simpson announces his plans to retire.</span>
                </div> 
                <br> 
                <a href="http://www.passcal.nmt.edu/content/seismic-community-gathers-sits"><strong><span style="color:#4b0082;">SITS Workshop A Success</span></strong></a>
                <br> 
                <br> 
                <span style="font-size:8pt;">The Seismic Instrumentation Technology Symposium was held&nbsp;June&nbsp;10–11&nbsp;in Alubuquerque, NM.</span>
               </div> 
               <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                <br> 
                <div style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #000000; line-height: 13px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12px"> 
                 <br> 
                 <a href="http://www.obsip.org/about/2013-obs-workshop/"><span style="color:#4b0082;"><strong>OBSIP Workshop</strong></span></a>
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;">October 21–22, 2013<br> Redondo Beach, CA</span>
                 <br> 
                 <span style="font-size:8pt;">Register now to participate.</span>
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <br> 
                 <a href="http://www.iris.edu/hq/employment"><strong style="color: rgb(75, 0, 130);">Job Opportunities</strong></a>
